    "faq_sc": {
      "type": "faq-accordion-section",
      "blocks": {
        "cat_sc1": {
          "type": "category",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Skin & Coat"
          }
        },
        "faq_sc1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long before I see results?",
            "content": "<p>Most dogs show noticeable improvements in coat shine and reduced shedding within 4-6 weeks of consistent daily use. For dry or irritated skin, some pet parents notice relief sooner.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_sc2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this safe for dogs with fish allergies?",
            "content": "<p>Our Skin &amp; Coat chews contain fish oil as the primary Omega-3 source. If your dog has a known fish allergy, please consult your veterinarian before use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_sc3": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I give this alongside other supplements?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. TailSpark Skin &amp; Coat can be combined with our other supplements. If combining with other Omega-3 sources, consult your vet about total daily intake.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_sc4": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What age dogs can take these?",
            "content": "<p>Suitable for dogs 6 months and older. For puppies under 6 months or dogs with specific health conditions, please consult your veterinarian.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_sc5": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will Skin & Coat help with my dog's itching and allergies?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. The Omega-3 fatty acids from fish oil are well-documented for reducing skin inflammation, which relieves itching and irritation. Biotin and Vitamin E further support skin barrier function. Many pet parents see noticeable relief from dry, itchy skin within 3-4 weeks of daily use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_sc6": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does shipping take?",
            "content": "<p>All orders ship free with no minimum purchase. Processing takes 1-2 business days and delivery typically arrives within 5-6 business days. You will receive a tracking number by email once your order ships. Contact our support team if your order has not arrived after 8 business days.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_sc7": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer a subscription plan?",
            "content": "<p>Yes! Subscribe &amp; Save gives you 15% off every delivery automatically plus free shipping every time. Skin and coat health improves with consistent daily nutrition, so subscribing is the best way to maintain results long-term. You can skip, pause, or cancel anytime with no hassle.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
